.TH "drm_mode_get_hv_timing" 9 "drm_mode_get_hv_timing" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_mode_get_hv_timing \- Fetches hdisplay/vdisplay for given mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" drm_mode_get_hv_timing
.BI "(const struct drm_display_mode *mode "  ","
.BI "int *hdisplay "  ","
.BI "int *vdisplay "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mode" 12
mode to query
.IP "hdisplay" 12
hdisplay value to fill in
.IP "vdisplay" 12
vdisplay value to fill in
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
The vdisplay value will be doubled if the specified mode is a stereo mode of
the appropriate layout.
